 None is individually very famous."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Mary Farr was christened on 9 June 1600, in Great Burstead, Essex, England, United Kingdom as the daughter of Henry Farr. She married Robert Farr in England. They were the parents of at least 1 son and 1 daughter."},"et":{"09 JUN 1600–":"9. juuni 1600–Surnud","1600–Female":"1600–Surnud","1595–1657":"1595–1657","1615–Female":"1615–Surnud","1621–Male":"1621–Surnud","–Male":"Surnud","1657":"1657","1600":"1600","1621":"1621","1595":"1595","22 OCT 1615":"22. oktoober 1615","11 November 1621":"11. november 1621","1615":"1615","09 JUN 1600":"9. juuni 1600","Kingsbridge, Devonshire, England, United Kingdom":"Kingsbridge, Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","England":"England","Great Burstead,Essex,England":"Great Burstead, Essex, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Kingsbridge,Devon,England":"Kingsbridge, Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"09 JUN 1600–":"9. kesäkuuta 1600–Kuollut","1600–Female":"1600–Kuollut","1595–1657":"1595–1657","1615–Female":"1615–Kuollut","1621–Male":"1621–Kuollut","–Male":"Kuollut","1657":"1657","1600":"1600","1621":"1621","1595":"1595","22 OCT 1615":"22. lokakuuta 1615","11 November 1621":"11. marraskuuta 1621","1615":"1615","09 JUN 1600":"9. kesäkuuta 1600","Kingsbridge, Devonshire, England, United Kingdom":"Kingsbridge, Devon, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","England":"England","Great Burstead,Essex,England":"Great Burstead, Essex, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Kingsbridge,Devon,England":"Kingsbridge, Devon, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"09 JUN 1600–":"9 juin 1600–Décédée","1600–Female":"1600–Décédée","1595–1657":"1595–1657","1615–Female":"1615–Décédée","1621–Male":"1621–Décédé","–Male":"Décédé","1657":"1657","1600":"1600","1621":"1621","1595":"1595","22 OCT 1615":"22 octobre 1615","11 November 1621":"11 novembre 1621","1615":"1615","09 JUN 1600":"9 juin 1600","Kingsbridge, Devonshire, England, United Kingdom":"Kingsbridge, Devon, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","England":"Angl